# don't auto-rebuild the dev env when flake.nix changes. use_flake always watches
# flake.nix, and a rebuild re-archives all ~80 flake inputs as gc roots (~6s), which
# we'd otherwise pay on every save. with manual reload an out-of-date cache just warns
# and keeps the old env; run `nix-direnv-reload` by hand after a real input change.
nix_direnv_manual_reload
use flake
